== 法語加勒比地區 ==
'''法語加勒比地區'''是指西印度群島上講[[法语|法語]]或[[克里奧爾語|克里奧爾語]]的地區。<ref>{{cite web|title=Food Culture in the Caribbean|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZZEeyKrytcwC&pg=PR21&lpg=PR21&dq=French+Caribbean+haiti&source=bl&ots=y0-6iXqgNA&sig=46YI5zIi2n1jUwodv3VrpKhk4fE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=PLYIVcrXCZSLsQTAtYDwCw&ved=0CDcQ6AEwBTgK#v=onepage&q=French%20Caribbean%20haiti&f=false|accessdate=17 March 2015|author=Houston, Lynn Marie|year=2005|page=xxi|isbn=0313327645|archive-date=2020-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913224205/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZZEeyKrytcwC&pg=PR21&lpg=PR21&dq=French%20Caribbean%20haiti&source=bl&ots=y0-6iXqgNA&sig=46YI5zIi2n1jUwodv3VrpKhk4fE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=PLYIVcrXCZSLsQTAtYDwCw&ved=0CDcQ6AEwBTgK#v=onepage&q=French%20Caribbean%20haiti&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=France and the Americas: Culture, Politics, and History|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jfq5Tp0nq98C&pg=PA17&lpg=PA17&dq=the+french+caribbean+haiti+guadeloupe+martinique&source=bl&ots=BKlnjZyI8m&sig=soCu5Of0PHIO3jSJwVZh7BBA0Ns&hl=en&sa=X&ei=CMMIVYwZi-ewBL7MgbAJ&ved=0CEcQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=the%20french%20caribbean%20haiti%20guadeloupe%20martinique&f=false|accessdate=17 March 2015|author=Johnston, Christina|year=2005|page=17|isbn=1851094113|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831022636/https://books.google.com/books?id=jfq5Tp0nq98C&pg=PA17&lpg=PA17&dq=the%20french%20caribbean%20haiti%20guadeloupe%20martinique&source=bl&ots=BKlnjZyI8m&sig=soCu5Of0PHIO3jSJwVZh7BBA0Ns&hl=en&sa=X&ei=CMMIVYwZi-ewBL7MgbAJ&ved=0CEcQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=the%20french%20caribbean%20haiti%20guadeloupe%20martinique&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Crossroads of Empire: The European-Caribbean Connection, 1492-1992|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IalxKZ_YBMQC&pg=PA1&dq=francophone+caribbean+haiti&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CEoQ6AEwB2oVChMI_euBpsyMyAIVyj0-Ch0ysgQD#v=onepage&q=francophone%20caribbean%20haiti&f=false|accessdate=23 September 2015|author=Cobley, Alan Gregor|page=1|isbn=9766210314|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001031257/https://books.google.com/books?id=IalxKZ_YBMQC&pg=PA1&dq=francophone%20caribbean%20haiti&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CEoQ6AEwB2oVChMI_euBpsyMyAIVyj0-Ch0ysgQD#v=onepage&q=francophone%20caribbean%20haiti&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>該地區是[[法語美洲|法語美洲]]的組成部分之一。

法語加勒比地區的含義要被法屬安的斯列要含糊，因爲前者意指西印度群島中所有受法國文化影響的地區<ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/popularmusicsofn0000manu|url-access=registration|quote=carabinier martinique.|title=Popular Musics of the Non-Western World: An Introductory Survey|publisher=Oxford University Press|author=Manuel, Peter|pages=[https://archive.org/details/popularmusicsofn0000manu/page/72 72]|year=1988|isbn=0195053427|accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>，而後者則爲直屬法國的行政區域。

